            ],
            "stanza_text": "Expert en les dialectiques,\nTu parles et tu sophistiques\nAvec ta voix de clair métal :\nEt les tentations pullulent,\nEt les tentations ululent\nDans l'ombre du ravin fatal."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Car tu sais pour damner notre âme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "10"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Faire jaillir la pure-flamme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "11"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Dans l'œil des hiboux et des freux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "12"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tu connais les accoutumances",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "13"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Des devins, et les nigromances",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "13"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et les hocuspocus affreux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "12"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car tu sais pour damner notre âme\nFaire jaillir la pure-flamme\nDans l'œil des hiboux et des freux ;\nTu connais les accoutumances\nDes devins, et les nigromances\nEt les hocuspocus affreux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Sous la comète et sous la lune,",
