                    "line_text": "De nos vœux tu guides l'essor",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "19"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Où, dans sa fière nonchalance,",
