                    "line_text": "La fleur-charnelle se balance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "20"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Pareille au grand lis nimbé d'or.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "19"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "À travers les chaudes haleines.\nDes tabacs et des marjolaines,\nDe nos vœux tu guides l'essor\nOù, dans sa fière nonchalance,\nLa fleur-charnelle se balance\nPareille au grand lis nimbé d'or."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Mais ta promesse n'est que leurre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "21"
                },
                {
